        <mj-title>Rapid Information Systems: A Double Nominee in June’s Awards Season</mj-title>
        <mj-preview>Welcome to our latest newsletter from Rapid! Dive into this edition to discover the latest updates, insightful articles, and innovative features shaping the future of software solutions. Stay connected with us as we continue to redefine possibilities in the digital landscape for the public sector.</mj-preview>
